    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.1",
          "pli": "“Rūpā, bhikkhave, aniccā. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, sights are impermanent. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.2",
          "pli": "Yopi hetu, yopi paccayo rūpānaṃ uppādāya, sopi anicco. ",
          "en": "The cause and condition that gives rise to sights is also impermanent. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.3",
          "pli": "Aniccasambhūtā, bhikkhave, rūpā kuto niccā bhavissanti. ",
          "en": "Since sights are produced by what is impermanent, how could they be permanent? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.4",
          "pli": "Saddā … ",
          "en": "Sounds … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.5",
          "pli": "gandhā … ",
          "en": "Smells … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.6",
          "pli": "rasā … ",
          "en": "Tastes … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.7",
          "pli": "phoṭṭhabbā … ",
          "en": "Touches … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.8",
          "pli": "dhammā aniccā. ",
          "en": "Thoughts are impermanent. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.9",
          "pli": "Yopi hetu, yopi paccayo dhammānaṃ uppādāya, sopi anicco. ",
          "en": "The cause and condition that gives rise to thoughts is also impermanent. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.10",
          "pli": "Aniccasambhūtā, bhikkhave, dhammā kuto niccā bhavissanti. ",
          "en": "Since thoughts are produced by what is impermanent, how could they be permanent? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.11",
          "pli": "Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … ",
          "en": "Seeing this … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.12",
          "pli": "nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. ",
          "en": "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn35.143:1.13",
          "pli": "Dasamaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
